OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FA man who was paralysed from the neck
OL,7,Fdown by a rare autoimmune disorder
OL,8,Fdefied doctors by "proudly" walking
OL,9,Fout of hospital following life-saving
OL,10,Fplasma treatment.
OL,12,FCancer survivor Tony Newitt feared he
OL,13,Fwould never get to meet his grandchild
OL,14,Fafter being diagnosed with Guillain-
OL,15,FBarre Syndrome (GBS) last year.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FThe 71-year-old, from Alcester in
OL,7,FWarwickshire, is now urging more
OL,8,Fpeople to donate plasma after telling
OL,9,Fhis family the treatments are the
OL,10,F"only reason" he has been able to
OL,11,Fbegin to rebuild his life.
OL,13,FHis daughter Lauren Marshall also
OL,14,Fhailed plasma as "liquid gold" and is
OL,15,Fnow a regular donor herself.
OL,17,FMr Newitt was diagnosed with bowel and
OL,18,Fliver cancer in 2024, and, after
OL,19,Fintense treatment, scans showed no
OL,20,Fsigns of the disease.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]vD@ROUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FHowever, in March 2025, weeks after
OL,7,Fhis last chemotherapy session, he
OL,8,Fcollapsed at home putting the bins out.
OL,10,FMedics were initially baffled by what
OL,11,Fcould have caused Mr Newitt's
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,FMs Marshall, 37, who was pregnant with
OL,15,Fher daughter Isabelle at the time,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The staff in hospital didn't
OL,17,Fknow what had happened because it was
OL,18,Fjust like somebody had flipped the
OL,19,Fswitch and he just had lost all use of
OL,20,Fhis body.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,F"We all thought it might be brain
OL,7,Fcancer pushing on a particular part of
OL,8,Fhis brain and causing him to not be
OL,9,Fable to use his legs. It was all very
OL,10,Fscary."
OL,12,FMr Newitt's oncologist eventually
OL,13,Fsuggested he may have GBS, which was
OL,14,Fconfirmed by a lumbar puncture.
OL,16,FGBS is a rare condition that is
OL,17,Fthought to be caused by an
OL,18,Foverreaction of the immune system.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
