FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FAccording to NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,7,F(NHSBT), more than 3,200 patients have
OL,8,Fhad immunoglobulin medicines made from
OL,9,FUK-donated plasma since March.
OL,11,FIt comes five years after a ban on the
OL,12,Fuse of UK plasma was lifted.
OL,14,FThe ban was brought in in 1998 due to
OL,15,Fconcerns over Creutzfeldt-Jakob
OL,16,Fdisease, or mad cow disease.
OL,18,FThe UK now meets 23% of NHS
OL,19,Fimmunoglobulin demand, but still
OL,20,Frelies on imports, primarily from the
OL,21,FUS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
