OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FNHSBT is hoping to boost the figure to
OL,12,F35% by 2030.
OL,14,FMs Marshall, who has been a blood
OL,15,Fdonor for two decades after losing a
OL,16,Fclose friend in a car accident,
OL,17,Fswitched to donating plasma after her
OL,18,Ffather's experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
