FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781444875
OL,3,C'Liquid gold' plasma treatment helps
OL,4,Cparalysed man walk out of hospital
OL,6,FShe said: "My dad categorically said
OL,7,Fthat the plasma that he received was
OL,8,Fthe only reason he was able to leave
OL,9,Fhospital and begin to rebuild his life.
OL,11,F"He says it was the 'liquid gold' that
OL,12,Fgave him his life back."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOU
